OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,FThe public may need to be
OL,7,F'incentivised' not to travel by train
OL,8,Ffollowing the axing of the northern
OL,9,Fleg of HS2, according to a government
OL,10,Fwatchdog.
OL,12,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) says
OL,13,Fthat 'capacity issues' will mean that
OL,14,Fthe current situation where travellers
OL,15,Fnorth of Birmingham will use the West
OL,16,FCoast Mainline (WCML) may save time
OL,17,Fbut won't make for easier journeys.
