OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,FIn October 2023 then Prime Minister
OL,7,FRishi Sunak announced that the HS2
OL,8,Fhigh speed line would not be extended
OL,9,Fto Manchester.
OL,11,FAccording to the NAO this could mean
OL,12,Fthat rail users will face HS2 trains
OL,13,Fwith fewer seats unless stations and
OL,14,Finfrastructure are upgraded to
OL,15,Faccommodate longer trains.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
