OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,FIt went on: "This may constrain
OL,7,Feconomic growth in the region over the
OL,8,Flong term and increase environmental
OL,9,Fcosts".
OL,11,FAnother possibility could be improving
OL,12,For adding infrastructure but "this may
OL,13,Fbe expensive and disruptive",
OL,14,Faccording to the watchdog.
OL,16,FThe report also found it could cost
OL,17,FHS2 Ltd up to #100 million and take up
OL,18,Fto three years to scale back its plans
OL,19,Ffollowing Mr Sunak's decision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
