OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,FThe process involves decommissioning
OL,7,Fand closing down construction sites,
OL,8,Fand reinstating land to its original
OL,9,Fstate.
OL,11,FA spokesman for HS2 Ltd said: "This is
OL,12,Fa project of unprecedented scale and
OL,13,Fcomplexity, and the cancellation of
OL,14,FPhase 2 has increased our cost
OL,15,Fchallenges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
