OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,F"We are now making sweeping reforms to
OL,7,Fcontrol costs better and deliver the
OL,8,Fnext stage of the programme - passing
OL,9,Fpeak construction between London and
OL,10,Fthe West Midlands, and starting the
OL,11,Ftransition to a working railway."
OL,13,FThe government has been quick to point
OL,14,Fits finger at its predecessors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
