OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh said:
OL,7,F"It's long been clear that the
OL,8,FConservatives recklessly mismanaged
OL,9,FHS2 and allowed the costs to spiral
OL,10,Fentirely out of control - but this
OL,11,Freport lays bare the scale of their
OL,12,Fmistakes.
OL,14,F"We are reviewing this report's
OL,15,Ffindings, alongside the position we
OL,16,Fhave inherited on HS2 and wider
OL,17,Ftransport infrastructure, and will set
OL,18,Fout next steps in due course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
