OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,F"Transport is an essential part of our
OL,7,Fmission to rebuild Britain ` and we're
OL,8,Fcommitted to delivering infrastructure
OL,9,Fthat works for the whole country."
OL,11,FThe DfT have not commented, but
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,13,Fsays he has been vindicated by the
OL,14,Freport.
OL,16,FIn a statement he says: "The report
OL,17,Ffrom the National Audit Office (NAO)
OL,18,Fshines a spotlight on the consequences
OL,19,Fof cancelling the northern leg of HS2
OL,20,Fand backs up what we have been saying.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
