OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,F"By the Department for Transport's
OL,7,Fassessment, the West Coast Main Line
OL,8,Fwill be at capacity by the mid-2030s.
OL,9,FNot doing anything to address this
OL,10,Fwould be a brake on growth.
OL,12,F"As Mayor of Greater Manchester, I
OL,13,Fwill never accept a message to the
OL,14,Fpublic of "don't travel to Greater
OL,15,FManchester by rail".
OL,17,F"Anyone who currently travels on the
OL,18,FWest Coast Main Line on a regular
OL,19,Fbasis knows how chaotic it can be. It
OL,20,Fcannot take all those additional HS2
OL,21,Ftrains in its current state.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
