OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,F"As the NAO points out, they would
OL,7,Fhave to be shorter trains, so there
OL,8,Fwould be fewer seats, and they would
OL,9,Fgo slower.
OL,11,F"The idea that we are going to make
OL,12,Frail services worse by the middle of
OL,13,Fthe century is a complete non-starter
OL,14,F` a different plan is needed. This is
OL,15,Fan urgent problem that needs a
OL,16,Fcoherent solution.
OL,18,F"No-one is talking about going back to
OL,19,FHS2, but there has to be additional
OL,20,Fcapacity between the West Midlands and
OL,21,FGreater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
