OL,3,CRail users face 'don't travel' message
OL,4,Cafter axing of HS2 watchdog warns
OL,6,F"This could be done through expanding
OL,7,Fand upgrading the West Coast Main
OL,8,FLine, although the NAO warns that this
OL,9,Fwould be very disruptive. I see a new,
OL,10,Flower-cost, dedicated line as the only
OL,11,Freal solution.
OL,13,F"It would therefore be a mistake for
OL,14,Fthe government to have a fire sale of
OL,15,Fthe land it has bought to build HS2.
OL,16,FAround #600m has already been spent,
OL,17,Fthere is no way the government would
OL,18,Frecover that value. The best thing is
OL,19,Fto use that land to pave the way for
OL,20,Fthe new line."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
